'''''Long Arm of the Godfather''''' ({{lang-it|La mano lunga del padrino}}) is a 1972 Italian [[crime film]] directed by [[Nardo Bonomi]] and starring [[Adolfo Celi]].<ref name="NY Times">{{cite web |url=http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/122482/The-Long-Arm-of-the-Godfather/overview |title=New York Times: Long Arm of the Godfather |accessdate=2008-08-31|work=NY Times}}</ref>

